<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Materials.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Five specimens found in mosses on rock from Southwest China (YN5) (Table 
<tableCitation captionStart="Table 2" captionStartId="T2" captionText="Table 2. Sampling locality information of this survey." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/14C6D5980EAD552759DE04418B45F3F2" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" tableUuid="14C6D5980EAD552759DE04418B45F3F2">2</tableCitation>
